OL,5, The Liberal Democrats are calling for a
OL,6, higher minimum wage for social care    
OL,7, workers to help tackle staff shortages.
OL,9,FUnder the party's proposals, staff     
OL,10,Fwould be paid at least #2 an hour more 
OL,11,Fthan the minimum wage - currently #9.50
OL,12,Fan hour for over-23s.                  
OL,14,FLib Dem leader Sir Ed Davey said the   
OL,15,Fmove would "prevent the exodus of      
OL,16,Fworkers" to better paid jobs.          
OL,18,FThe party said the government would    
OL,19,Fneed to give councils an extra #1bn a  
OL,20,Fyear to cover higher staffing costs.   
